{"id": 1029, "genre": 1001, "title": "六一到了，我们来谈谈你都受够了哪些熊孩子？", "description": "研究所陪你欢度佳节。（题图来自：filip posivac）", "record_count": 5258, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201607031301118Weu0sfvFgXzd32i.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-06-01T11:01:05Z", "options": [{"id": 83712, "content": "爸妈的“他还只是个孩子，什么都不懂”", "image": null, "praise_count": 697, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 83713, "content": "“不就是个玩具吗，送给他不就得了”", "image": null, "praise_count": 529, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 83970, "content": "我作为一个狗狗主人，对那些恶意调戏宠物的熊孩子忍无可忍，曾经还对着一个孩子破口大骂。", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 540792}, {"id": 86020, "content": "“我们家孩子吵到你们了吧？”然后继续每天在楼上砰砰砰邦邦邦哐哐哐地震一样。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 637592}, {"id": 83973, "content": "没生娃之前觉得所有孩子都是烦人的熊孩子，生了娃之后觉得除了自己的其他所有都是熊孩子", "image": null, "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 403395}, {"id": 83975, "content": "爱哭的", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 628715}, {"id": 83976, "content": "砸我东西我都可以忍，欺负我的猫主子我跟你爸妈拼命", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 346805}, {"id": 115468, "content": "随意拿你的东西随意破坏你心爱的玩意，然后还不能教育。心累", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 755861}, {"id": 83981, "content": "我就喜欢这个板块，彩色的，看的高兴！", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 606266}, {"id": 83983, "content": "不直接说想要，问哥哥这是什么? ……我特么又不认识你", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 272649}, {"id": 83984, "content": "可以说受够了熊孩子的家长吗？没有熊家长就没有熊孩子...", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 631199}, {"id": 83987, "content": "小小年纪就开始爆粗口", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 501450}, {"id": 84756, "content": "公共场合大哭大闹", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 616605}, {"id": 89108, "content": "在吃饭等公众场合吵闹 超级吵 鸡毛蒜皮大声哭....真的好烦", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 646515}, {"id": 83989, "content": "高铁火车上由奶奶爷爷带着出门的熊孩子 都不坐好就喊着找妈妈", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 603635}, {"id": 89109, "content": "没礼貌！学大人骂脏话", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 646515}, {"id": 83990, "content": "熊孩子弄坏了贵重物品——孩子嘛，让这点怎么了……（呵呵）", "image": null, "praise_count": 33, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 507487}, {"id": 83991, "content": "满口脏话，家长却说孩子小，没事儿", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 630530}, {"id": 83992, "content": "尖叫", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 547590}, {"id": 83994, "content": "本来是他做错事却一定要说是你做的?", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 605884}, {"id": 83995, "content": "神经吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 486745}, {"id": 83996, "content": "一玩起来就没个够", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 623041}, {"id": 83997, "content": "“不给我玩电脑，我这杯水就浇进去。”", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 336202}, {"id": 83998, "content": "越看越生气\r\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 265401}, {"id": 84000, "content": "反客为主，肆意妄为，霸占电视机", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 164080}, {"id": 84001, "content": "总是无端白事喜欢大声叫嚷的………", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 618560}, {"id": 84002, "content": "这个电视不好看，我要看熊出没…这个游戏不好玩，我要玩生死狙击", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 538207}, {"id": 84003, "content": "会翻白眼的小孩", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 622138}, {"id": 84004, "content": "没遇到什么熊孩子诶，", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 613937}, {"id": 84005, "content": "熊孩子说我是朋友的阿姨，还说我摘了眼睛很漂亮，戴眼镜很丑（以童言无忌的角度分析，可能真的是因为我长得丑(・-・*) 当时我朋友笑炸，我尴尬的想把熊孩子打一顿，还是男性朋友呢）", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 629814}, {"id": 84006, "content": "商场里竟躲孩子玩了…", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 352921}, {"id": 84007, "content": "死缠着不放的", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 631287}, {"id": 84009, "content": "对熊孩子没意见，但极度讨厌熊父母", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 387294}, {"id": 84010, "content": "孩子嘛 小  还什么都不懂呢", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 631289}, {"id": 84012, "content": "偷偷摸摸拿我东西并且毁坏弄丢或者说是我让他拿的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 266160}, {"id": 84013, "content": "不多说，所有…", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 245267}, {"id": 84014, "content": "他们觉得什么都应该是无条件属于自己的！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 263377}, {"id": 84015, "content": "在外婆面前永远没有错，根本教育不得，外婆还很险碰坏我们孩子怎", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 611878}, {"id": 84016, "content": "小孩打人都是下死力气！", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 589115}, {"id": 84017, "content": "先吃饱再干活", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 501408}, {"id": 84018, "content": "不停的撒娇的孩子", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 610639}, {"id": 84275, "content": "我想试试我可以写多少个字还吃爱吃彼此彼此哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈还哈哈咳咳吃啊哈哈和哈哈哈哈和哈呵哈哈哈哈哈 hi 啊哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈呵哈哈怕哈哈哈呵呵呵呵哈呵啊哈哈哈哈哈哈和海带啊哈哈哈呵呵呵额呵哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 518854}, {"id": 84020, "content": "在病房的走廊上疯跑…", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 594498}, {"id": 84021, "content": "乱翻我书柜的?", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 612973}, {"id": 84022, "content": "真有爱", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 631430}, {"id": 84023, "content": "喜欢玩粘苍蝇纸的小男孩用它堵在门口不让进门", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 359965}, {"id": 84024, "content": "不洗澡不睡觉精神倍爽", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 605853}, {"id": 84025, "content": "舞剧当儿童剧看，我看过一边演出一边讲解", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 631496}, {"id": 84281, "content": "讨厌所有比我小5岁以上的人，不管熊不熊......", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 512237}, {"id": 84026, "content": "看电影误去了熊孩子专场", "image": "img/option/option/20160702183055DhU1ocNbVKRPeGvJ.jpg", "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 401406}]}